examples.en: Passing traffic has spattered the wall with mud.
The dog jumped in the pool and spattered us with water.
examples.ru: Собака прыгнула в бассейн и забрызгала нас водой.

examples.en: Mistakes were spattered throughout the whole article.
Be careful with that brush, you're spattering paint on / over the floor.
examples.ru: Будь аккуратнее с этой кисточкой: ты брызгаешь краской на пол.

examples.en: The baby spattered the bib with food.
She placed a cover over the pan so that the oil wouldn't spatter.
examples.ru: Она накрыла кастрюлю крышкой, чтобы масло не брызгало.

examples.en: The walls were spattered with placards.
There were grease spatters all over the wall.
examples.ru: По всей стене были брызги смазки.

examples.en: The floor was covered with spatters of paint.
He showed me how to use the paintbrush so the paint wouldn't spatter.
examples.ru: Он показал мне, как использовать кисть, чтобы краска не разбрызгивалась.
